      • Book

        public Book(long id,
            String fileName,
            String title,
            String author)
        Creates a Book object which stores information about a Book in the library
        Parameters:
        id - the unique primary key of the book in the database
        fileName - the file name used to access the book on the phone
        title - the title of the book used for sorting and display purposes
        author - the author of the book used for sorting and display purposes

      • Book

        public Book(String fileName,
            String title,
            String author)
        Create a Book object which stores information about a Book in the library. The id is automatically assigned by the database.
        Parameters:
        fileName - the file name used to access the book on the phone
        title - the title of the book used for sorting and display purposes
        author - the author of the book used for sorting and display purposes
